    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about-section text-center" style="background-image: url(../img/bg_covid.png);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-white mb-4">A small effort of my soul.</h2>
                    <p class="text-white-50">
                        Since we all have been locked down into our homes due to COVID 19, we may be wondering why this pandemic has been a pain in our ass.
                        We might not have faced this kind of epidemic over this decade, however, we can still recall back the times when our world communities
                        faced the deadly virus of that period like ebola and all. Unlike our country where epidemics like cholera and malaria kill hundreds of
                        people in a year, for us its like a bug in our nose. Here's what it's like to be at home during these
                        <a href="#">hard times</a>. During this period, we can help each other staying at our home, conversing with strangers (ref. parents) who had been living with us for
                        lifetimes, making good use of yourself at daily chores, and everything you want that you weren't able to do before. Stay Safe! Stay Clean! Peace!
                    </p>
