                        <h4>Bhatbhateni</h4>
                        <p class="text-black-50 mb-0">
                            Bhatbhateni, one of the best supermarkets in Nepal basically known for the better customer service and hospitality, offers a variety of services including home delivery of the necessary items. The delivery service was in action to reduce the crowd at the shopping malls which in turn helps Nepalese to be free from the possible contamination of Covid 19 at public places. People can register into the Bhatbhateni mobile app and cart the necessary items during their stay at home. This is a remarkable effort from the commercialized shopping complex which has been making an effort for the betterment and healthy living of its customers.
                        </p>
